MazeSimulation.RobotType
 
MemoryRobot
The MazeSimulation.MemoryRobot class represents a robot that will remember each tile it has stepped on and will not go on a tile more than once unless it is backtracking.
Position
The MazeSimulation.Position class represents a positive integer based position in 2D.
RandomRobot
The MazeSimulation.RandomRobot class represents a robot that will randomly traverse a MazeSimulation.Maze.
RightHandRuleRobot
The RightHandRobot class represents a robot that will traverse a MazeSimulation.Maze follow the path of wall to its right.

Interface for the MazeSimulation.Robot classes.
